  {
    "id": "4238c437-8a37-4827-98be-700ff6a3585c",
    "name": "Oferta 2026",
    "description": "Oferta A4 z okładką po 3 wina na stronę",
    "category": "general",
    "htmlContent": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"pl\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n\n<style>\n@page { size: A4; margin: 0; }\n\nhtml, body {\n  margin: 0;\n  padding: 0;\n  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n}\n\n/* Okładka - zawsze pierwsza strona */\n.cover-page {\n  width: 210mm;\n  height: 297mm;\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  align-items: center;\n  justify-content: center;\n  background-size: cover;\n  background-position: center;\n  box-sizing: border-box;\n  /* ✅ Wymuszenie nowej strony po okładce - WAŻNE! */\n  page-break-after: always;\n  break-after: page;\n  page-break-inside: avoid;\n  break-inside: avoid;\n}\n\n.cover-title {\n  font-size: 36pt;\n  font-weight: bold;\n  color: white;\n  text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.8);\n  text-align: center;\n  padding: 30mm;\n  z-index: 10;\n  position: relative;\n}\n\n.cover-image {\n  max-width: 90%;\n  max-height: 90%;\n  height: auto;\n  border-radius: 8px;\n \n}\n\n/* ✅ Strona z winami - FLEX zamiast grid-template-rows */\n.page {\n  width: 210mm;\n  height: 297mm;\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: column;\n  page-break-after: always;\n  break-after: page;\n  page-break-inside: avoid;\n  break-inside: avoid;\n  box-sizing: border-box;\n}\n\n/* Header - stała wysokość */\n.header {\n  background: #000000;\n  color: #ffffff;\n  height: 30mm;\n  flex-shrink: 0;\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  padding: 0 15mm;\n  font-size: 18pt;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  box-sizing: border-box;\n}\n  \n  .footer{\n   background: #f5f5f5;\n  color: #ffffff;\n  height: 15mm;\n     display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  padding: 0 15mm;\n  }\n\n/* ✅ Wiersz z winem - każdy zajmuje 1/3 pozostałej wysokości */\n.wine-row {\n  flex: 1;\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: 40mm 1fr; /* obrazek + treść */\n  gap: 8mm;\n  padding: 8mm 15mm;\n  border-top: 0.3mm solid #000;\n  box-sizing: border-box;\n  overflow: hidden;       /* ✅ zabezpiecza przed \"wypychem\" na kolejną stronę */\n}\n\n/* Pudełko na obraz — stały rozmiar, żeby zawsze było w całości */\n.wine-imgbox {\n  width: 40mm;           /* tyle co kolumna obrazka */\n  height: 73mm;          /* dopasowane do layoutu */\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  justify-content: center;\n}\n\n/* Obraz ma się zmieścić w pudełku w całości */\n.wine-imgbox img {\n  max-width: 100%;\n  max-height: 100%;\n  width: auto;\n  height: auto;\n  object-fit: contain;\n  display: block;\n}\n\n/* Teksty */\n.wine-title {\n  margin: 2mm 0 2mm 0;\n  font-size: 13pt;\n}\n\n.wine-meta {\n  margin: 0 0 0.5mm 0;\n  font-size: 10pt;\n}\n\n.wine-desc {\n  margin: 2mm 0 2mm 0;\n  color:#888888;\n  font-size: 9.5pt;\n  line-height: 1.25;\n}\n  \n  .uwagi{\n  font-size: 7pt;\n     line-height: 1.25;\n    color:#888888;\n  }\n  \n  .logo img{\n  width:100px;\n  }\n</style>\n</head>\n\n<body>\n\n<!-- ✅ OKŁADKA - PIERWSZA STRONA -->\n\n  <div class=\"cover-page\" style=\"background-image: url('{{collection.coverImage}}');\">\n    <h1 class=\"cover-title\">{{collection.name}}</h1>\n  </div>\n\n\n<!-- ✅ STRONY Z WINAMI -->\n{{#each collection.winesByCategory}}\n  {{#each pages}}\n    <div class=\"page\">\n      <div class=\"header\"><div class=\"logo\" style=\"width:20%;\"><img src=\"https://witrynarium.pl/images/branding/Logo-white.png\">\n</div><div style=\"width:80%; text-align:right; text-transform: uppercase;\">Wina {{category}}</div></div>\n\n      {{#each this}}\n        <div class=\"wine-row\">\n          <div class=\"wine-imgbox\">\n            <img src=\"https://witrynarium.pl{{this.image}}\" alt=\"\">\n          </div>\n          <div>\n            <p class=\"wine-meta\"><strong>Nr kat:</strong> {{this.catalogNumber}}</p>\n            <h3 class=\"wine-title\">{{this.name}}</h3>\n            <p class=\"wine-meta\"><strong>Rodzaj wina i pojemność: </strong> {{this.category}} | {{this.type}} | {{this.customVolume}} ml</p>\n            <p class=\"wine-meta\"><strong>Producent:</strong> {{this.region}}</p>\n            <p class=\"wine-meta\"><strong>Szczep:</strong> {{this.szczepy}}</p>\n            <p class=\"wine-meta\"><strong>Region:</strong> {{this.region}}</p>\n            <p class=\"wine-meta\"><strong>Alk:</strong> {{this.alcohol}}</p>\n            <p class=\"wine-desc\">{{this.description}}</p>\n            <p class=\"wine-meta\"><strong>Cena:</strong>   {{#if this.customPrice}}\n            {{this.customPrice}} zł\n        {{else}}\n            {{this.price1}} zł\n        {{/if}}</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      {{/each}}\n\n      <div class=\"footer\"><p class=\"uwagi\">{{collection.uwagi}}</p></div> \n      \n    </div>\n    \n  \n  {{/each}}\n  \n \n  \n{{/each}}\n\n</body>\n</html>\n",
    "cssContent": "",
    "jsContent": "",
